:: Get through the door {"position":"2400,3100","size":"100,100"}
You run ahead as fast as you can and burst through the staff door, immediately you are lit up by the bright, yellowed, lights of the familiar hub-like area with the large gate and the bathrooms.

You turn towards the open staff door, seeing the creature almost momentarily stunned by the light too.
(if:not$HasInjury)[You slam the door shut, key it hand, knife in the other. The creature's footsteps thud louder and louder as you jam the keys into the door as quick as you can. You feel its weight hit against the door as you manage to turn the key, causing you to fall back, knife at the ready. To your relief, no matter how much the creature throws itself against the door, it cannot break through.]
(if:$HasInjury)[With the creature right on your tale, you turn, whipping the keys into your hand, ready to close and lock the staff door as quick as you can, but there isnt enough time! The creature shakes off the light, seemingly steaming like its burning in its touch as it reaches its claws out to you. You slam against the staff door to shut it, but the creature reaches its limb through the door to prevent it.
You push and push!! The creature rears its arm up and brings it down into your shoulder as you let out a screech, you see its skin splitting apart in the light however and you keep holding the door until finally it retracts its claws into the dark, allowing you to shut the door and lock it, hearing the creature whine and shriek as it retreats into the dark of the other side.

You take a moment to collect yourself, before letting yourself collapse onto the floor for a moment, out of breath and energy, you take this moment to rest.

(if:$HasInjury)[Your own blood covers you, you have multiple wounds, they're not deep, but not superficial either. You hold over them, keeping some pressure, to stop any mor bleeding; you barely came out of it all alive.

